#github注册选择学校邮箱，并记录双重登录，以确保后续获得github的教育优惠（双因素认证，github账单信息，摄像头提交学术隶属文件，录取信件）
Register for GitHub using your university email address and set up two-factor authentication (2FA) to ensure eligibility for GitHub’s student education benefits later. 
Required materials include two-factor authentication setup details, GitHub billing information, academic affiliation documents, and admission letter which need to be submitted via camera upload.

本课程对编程语言的要求，第一，Java 7（为简化赋值，不允许使用更高版本的 Java）第二，Java IDE（Eclipse 或 IntelliJ 可接受）第三，Git 和 GitHub第四，JUnit 3.8
codeLanguage requirements for this course:
Java 7 only.
Java IDE: Eclipse or IntelliJ IDEA are acceptable options.
